        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for CHB’s essay [<hi rend="italic">New observations on hay-fever</hi> (1877?)]. The calculation of the weight of pollen-grains is wonderful. Suggests he consult <hi rend="italic">Cross and self-fertilisation</hi>, pp. 376, 405 for information on this subject.</p> 
